item.title: Haybales
item.description: The haybales problem is from Bronze 1, December 2016. In this directory you can download the starter code. If you are new to Unix, you unpack it with the command tar zvxf usaco-y2016-m12.tar.bz2. Inside there is a README.md file that has a few more instructions.
